# energy-intel V2 editorial extension — KGCL change log
#
# Authored: 2026-05-04 by ontology-architect (V2 iteration)
# Source: docs/conceptualizer-to-architect-handoff-v2.md § 2 (axiom obligations A1..A12)
#         docs/axiom-plan-v2.md (CQ coverage map; SHACL S-V2-1..4)
# Materialized by: scripts/build_editorial.py (the source of truth) +
#                  scripts/extract_oeo_topic_subset.py (OEO subset rebuild).
#
# Curator audit: every cited source/target term in the blocks below resolves
# against the V2 closure (verified by `just validate-editorial` on
# 2026-05-04: ROBOT merge exit 0; HermiT reason exit 0; ROBOT report 0
# project-origin ERRORs after allowlist; pyshacl 11/11 fixtures pass;
# pytest 30/30 CQ tests pass).
#
# V1 baseline:
#   * Tag:           v0.2.0
#   * Commit:        1d8f9da  (release-time HEAD on `main` at V2 start)
#   * versionIRI:    https://w3id.org/energy-intel/v1/2026-04-27
#
# V2 release target:
#   * Tag:           v0.3.0
#   * versionIRI:    https://w3id.org/energy-intel/v2/2026-05-04
#
# These KGCL patches describe the structural changes between V1 and V2.
# They are recorded in KGCL form for human review and curator audit; the
# changes are materialised by `scripts/build_editorial.py`, not by
# `runoak apply` against this file. KGCL is the abstract specification
# layer; the build script is the runnable implementation.
#
# Each block is preceded by a short rationale and pinned to its V2 axiom
# obligation (A-row in the conceptualizer handoff).
#
# Apply only on a fresh checkout of V1 — running these against an
# already-V2 module set is a no-op (idempotent).

# ===================================================================
# A1 — Mint ei:Narrative
# ===================================================================
# Source: bfo-alignment-v2.md § 1; conceptualizer-to-architect-handoff-v2.md § 2 A1
# Module: modules/editorial.ttl (NEW)

create class https://w3id.org/energy-intel/Narrative label "narrative"@en
create edge https://w3id.org/energy-intel/Narrative rdfs:subClassOf http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000310
create definition "A written editorial unit about energy-domain events that have been curated by an editor. A Narrative groups posts that share an editorial through-line (a single argument or question) and applies an argument pattern to frame the discussion. Identified by a deterministic IRI derived from the story stem; the directory hierarchy on disk does not enter the IRI." for https://w3id.org/energy-intel/Narrative

# ===================================================================
# A2 — Mint ei:NarrativePostMembership
# ===================================================================
# Source: bfo-alignment-v2.md § 2; conceptualizer-to-architect-handoff-v2.md § 2 A2
# Module: modules/editorial.ttl

create class https://w3id.org/energy-intel/NarrativePostMembership label "narrative post membership"@en
create edge https://w3id.org/energy-intel/NarrativePostMembership rdfs:subClassOf http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000310
create definition "An information artefact recording that a Narrative includes a Post in a specific role (lead, supporting, counter, or context). One individual per (Narrative, Post) pair. Identified by a deterministic IRI derived from sha256 of (narrativeIri, postUri). Reified rather than four role-named predicates because role-named predicates would smuggle storage state into predicate names (System Blueprint anti-pattern), would not absorb future first-class qualifier storage cleanly, and would block the SHACL closed-shape invariant sh:qualifiedMaxCount 1 per (Narrative, Post)." for https://w3id.org/energy-intel/NarrativePostMembership

# ===================================================================
# A3 — DisjointClasses(Narrative, Post, PodcastEpisode, NarrativePostMembership)
# ===================================================================
# Source: anti-pattern-review-v2.md § 1 row 4 (defense-in-depth); conceptualizer-handoff-v2.md § 2 A3
# Module: modules/editorial.ttl

# (KGCL has no native AllDisjointClasses primitive; emitted by build_editorial.py
#  as an owl:AllDisjointClasses blank node with owl:members list. KGCL annotation:)
# disjoint classes ( https://w3id.org/energy-intel/Narrative https://w3id.org/energy-intel/Post https://w3id.org/energy-intel/PodcastEpisode https://w3id.org/energy-intel/NarrativePostMembership )

# ===================================================================
# A4 — Mint ei:hasNarrativePostMembership
# ===================================================================
# Source: property-design-v2.md § 1; conceptualizer-handoff-v2.md § 2 A4
# Module: modules/editorial.ttl

create object property https://w3id.org/energy-intel/hasNarrativePostMembership label "has narrative-post membership"@en
change object property domain https://w3id.org/energy-intel/hasNarrativePostMembership to https://w3id.org/energy-intel/Narrative
change object property range https://w3id.org/energy-intel/hasNarrativePostMembership to https://w3id.org/energy-intel/NarrativePostMembership

# ===================================================================
# A5 — Mint ei:memberPost (FunctionalProperty)
# ===================================================================
# Source: property-design-v2.md § 2; conceptualizer-handoff-v2.md § 2 A5
# Module: modules/editorial.ttl

create object property https://w3id.org/energy-intel/memberPost label "member post"@en
change object property domain https://w3id.org/energy-intel/memberPost to https://w3id.org/energy-intel/NarrativePostMembership
change object property range https://w3id.org/energy-intel/memberPost to https://w3id.org/energy-intel/Post
# (build_editorial.py emits owl:FunctionalProperty type triple)

# ===================================================================
# A6 — Mint ei:memberRole (FunctionalProperty)
# ===================================================================
# Source: property-design-v2.md § 3; conceptualizer-handoff-v2.md § 2 A6
# Module: modules/editorial.ttl

create object property https://w3id.org/energy-intel/memberRole label "member role"@en
change object property domain https://w3id.org/energy-intel/memberRole to https://w3id.org/energy-intel/NarrativePostMembership
change object property range https://w3id.org/energy-intel/memberRole to http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#Concept
# (build_editorial.py emits owl:FunctionalProperty type triple; SHACL S-V2-1 enforces sh:in over the 4 narrative-role concepts)

# ===================================================================
# A7 — Cardinality restriction on NarrativePostMembership for memberPost
# ===================================================================
# Source: property-design-v2.md § 2; axiom-plan-v2.md § 3 A7
# Module: modules/editorial.ttl
# (KGCL: owl:qualifiedCardinality restriction emitted by build_editorial.py)

# NarrativePostMembership rdfs:subClassOf [ owl:Restriction ; owl:onProperty ei:memberPost ; owl:qualifiedCardinality 1 ; owl:onClass ei:Post ]

# ===================================================================
# A8 — Cardinality restriction on NarrativePostMembership for memberRole
# ===================================================================
# Source: property-design-v2.md § 3; axiom-plan-v2.md § 3 A8
# Module: modules/editorial.ttl

# NarrativePostMembership rdfs:subClassOf [ owl:Restriction ; owl:onProperty ei:memberRole ; owl:qualifiedCardinality 1 ; owl:onClass skos:Concept ]

