# ===================================================================
# A12 — Max-cardinality restriction on Narrative for narrativeAppliesPattern
# ===================================================================
# Source: property-design-v2.md § 5; axiom-plan-v2.md § 3 A12
# Module: modules/editorial.ttl

# Narrative rdfs:subClassOf [ owl:Restriction ; owl:onProperty ei:narrativeAppliesPattern ; owl:maxQualifiedCardinality 1 ; owl:onClass skos:Concept ]

